      107.42,
      189.23,
      539.15,
      253.13
    ],
    "text": "Parallel to the investigation being conducted by the Galle Police Station into the fatal shooting incident that occurred in the Dangedara area within the Galle Police Division on 12 May 2026, the Walana Anti-Corruption Unit had also launched a separate investigation.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      267.71,
      533.39,
      331.52
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, on 23 May 2026, officers attached to the Walana Anti-Corruption Unit arrested two suspects alleged to have aided and abetted the crime. During the operation, police also recovered 12 grams and 260 milligrams of heroin from the possession of one of the suspects.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
